  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink236-kilavi">kaḷavoḻukkam veḷippaṭṭamaiyum tam melivum uṇarttit tōḻi uṭaṉpōkku nayantāḷ pōṉṟu varaivu kaṭāyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> Expressing the exposure of the clandestine union and their weakening, the confidante urges marriage, as though she wished [for their] elopement.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink236">
<l>aṉṉaiyu maṟintaṉa ḷalarumā yiṉṟu</l>
<l>naṉmaṉai neṭunakar pulampukoḷa vuṟutaru</l>
<l>miṉṉā vāṭaiyu malaiyu</l>
<l>nummūrc celka meḻukamō teyyō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Mother, too, knew; it also became gossip.</l>
        <l>The harsh northern winds, which grow excessive,</l>
        <l>so that the tall mansion of good household becomes desolate,</l>
        <l>will also oppose [us].</l>
        <l>Shall we rise to go to your town — alas?</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
